{"tid":1283943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2003年71父母抱住遊行既bb，就係2019年71戴頭盔衝立法會既年輕人","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:45:14.000Z","uid":33307,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7dab3d0e607dae4fd447a56aed9b5138b178f016","tid":1283943,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"時光飛逝<br />\n16年前香港創做左一次歷史<br />\n16年後我地面對緊更加惡劣既環境<br />\n冇主權，冇票，你每年都要遊行，示威<br />\n因為當權者利益與人民利益唔掛鉤<br />\n佢地永遠虎視眈眈點樣可以犧牲人民而取得利益<br />\n政府利益永遠同人民相反<br />\n<br />\n大家醒醒，我地冇幾多個16年<br />\n我地一定要爭取主權在民（我唔知應該係雙普定獨立）<br />\n今年帶小朋友遊行既人，都唔希望你仔女16年後又要戴頭盔，衝，比狗咬<br />\n希望大家唔好談判唔好妥協，直至得到永續民主，先算係有效結果"},{"pid":"5b2714db2a6af108307162e04d175b367520a0dc","tid":1283943,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:33:38.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"e3afb9b18328ad216e021c32c765000795c0a5fd","tid":1283943,"uid":123854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"3957ab5fad67a59fa742404cdc5a37e8ccb5b9fc","tid":1283943,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件</code></pre>"},{"pid":"72a77fd51a298131967f400cc3556aefb9f40cfa","tid":1283943,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"d4187e02b7c30fa2bf869988380e72003c1d4951","tid":1283943,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd1fada534d8889cc1c06132456f7275f577f56","tid":1283943,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"唔係，大把人父母係港豬/藍絲"},{"pid":"4b2c7bce34326